humanMachineDialogue.author: Memory Reasoning
humanMachineDialogue.text: According to the pathology report, 10 lymph nodes were examined and none of them were positive for metastasis (Axillary 0/10). Based on the new rules 10 and 11, N0 indicates no metastatic carcinoma in sentinel lymph nodes and regional lymph nodes or that all assessed lymph nodes are negative for metastatic carcinoma. Therefore, the N stage for this patient is N0.
